LOGIN














Amalgamated's proprietary titanium technology makes titanium consumer, military, and industrial products more affordable than ever before.











ABOUT AMALGAMATED




We are a specialty metals company based in Cambridge, MA that developed a cost-reducing titanium technology. Our proprietary technology allows our firm to manufacture titanium products cost-effectively. We can produce goods and sell them at a relative equivalent price to inferior material substitutes, such as high-grade steels and aluminums. Our company designs, manufactures, sells, and also licenses the highest quality titanium products at affordable prices. We design and create products for ourselves and for companies who will benefit from titanium's exceptional and unique attributes. We also stand by our titanium products with a lifetime guarantee.








SEPTEMBER 2016
Amalgamated at Quantico, VA
We were one of only 22 companies in the world to be invited by the Marine Corps to their annual Marksmanship Technology Demonstration (MTD). Held in September 2016, this three day event allowed the Marines, FBI, DEA, and Police officers to review and test Amalgamated arms. After a successful showing, Amalgamated Titanium was asked to sponsor the upcoming 3 Gun Competition in October, also to be held at the base in Quantico.
Read the full Story...



