ARMS PRODUCTS












Titanium
12G Pump Shotgun




This classic highly reliable 12-Gauge Pump Shotgun in titanium is exceptionally durable and 33% lighter than it's traditional counterparts. Due to it's light weight, this shotgun greatly eases the burden-of-carry and frees-up weight capacity  for soldiers and law enforcement. Standard finish for all titanium products is matte black. For titanium gray finish, the cost will be 50% higher.






