Titanium 12G Barrels




These titanium 12 gauge replacement barrels are 45% lighter than their steel counterparts found in legacy shotguns. Barrels include low profile, integrated (3/9/12 position) titanium Tri-Keymod Accessory Mount and muzzle Stand-Off. Compatible with select Remington, Mossberg & Benelli models. Standard finish for all titanium products is matte black. For titanium gray finish, the cost will be 50% higher.






