Titanium PDW




This compact AR-15 based PDW (personal defense weapon) in solid mil. spec. titanium is exceptionally durable and 33% lighter, while the 7” replacement barrels for legacy AR-15, are 45% lighter. Whether in need of an entire new titanium gun or titanium replacement barrel, both greatly ease the burden-of-carry. Available for Military & Law Enforcement only. Standard finish for all titanium products is matte black. For titanium gray finish, the cost will be 50% higher.





