Titanium Tactical Parts




Reduce the weight of your current or future AR-15 with these lightweight, 100% titanium components. They are 45% lighter than their steel equivalents. The Lower Receiver, Upper Receiver and Forend are all made from 6AL4V Titanium. The Forend is one piece, free float, top rail with tri-keymod. Standard finish for all titanium products is matte black. For titanium gray finish, the cost will be 50% higher.








