All products are made from mil. spec. Grade 5 titanium solid bar stock. Products are sold both standard mil. spec. and "on variance" custom orders. Any arms parts can be made for customers with our material, technology, and price advantage. All products available in Titanium finish or black anodized. Other finishes available on request. Due to high demand, we currently are not accepting custom orders of fewer than 5000 units.












FISHING












TITANIUM FISHING EQUIPMENT




Our titanium technology is being used by our subsidiary FORTiTUDE Fishing to create top of the line fishing equipment. Fortitude is the first fishing company ever to combine premier engineering and military spec titanium with affordable pricing. Whether a titanium reel, rod component, net or gaff, Fortitude makes high performance non-corrosive equipment that is the strongest, lightest, most durable on the market and we stand by it with a no compromise lifetime warranty.
 
Visit the fortitudefishing.com website to view the current product line...


















